  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a single momentary needle of darkness that erupts upwards from a creatures shadow that you can see within range. Make a ranged Genjutsu attack. On a hit you deal psychic damage equal to 4d6 + Your Genjutsu ability modifier and reducing their speed by 10 until the start of your next turn. A creature who's speed is reduced in this way cannot benefit from additional speed for the duration of their speed reduction.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the number of creatures you can target by +1, the damage by 1d6 and the speed reduction by -5.</p>",
